text: Riau Ega Agatha Salsabila is an Indonesian archer. He was born on 25 November 1991. Ega Agatha competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Riau Ega AgathaRiau EGA AGATHA == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia
